overview: Handsome, hot, hung, and insatiably horny, Elian is the whole package. When this Latin stud first debuted he was an instant hit, and he's not stopped winning over fans ever since. Elian demonstrated early on he loves sex, is darn good at it, and can't get enough of it. Develop your crush on Elian in his first, solo appearance at CF; fall for him even more as he rides Colt and feeds Dane, then embrace your Elian obsession as you see him in an epic threeway with Rocky and Dane in CF Crush: Elian.
title: CF Crush: Elian
